high_descs: Walk to the end of the counter by the coffee maker.
Pick up the sharp knife behind the sponge on the counter.
Take the sharp knife to the sink.
Slice the potato in the right side of the sink.
Look up at the sink.
Put the sharp knife down in the sink by the lettuce.
Look down at the sink.
Pick up a potato slice in the sink.
Walk to the microwave.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave.
Take the cooked potato slice to the counter by the coffee maker.
Set the cooked potato slice down in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right, facing the counter top with salt, a knife, and a bowl sitting on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter, in front of the black bowl.
Turn around and walk straight until you reach the sink on your right, then turn right to face the sink.
Cut the potato, located in front of the lettuce, in the right sink into slices.
Take a step closer to the sink, lifting the knife above the sink.
Place the knife in the same sink the lettuce and the potato are in.
Take one step back away from the sink.
Pick up one of the potato slices previously cut from the sink.
Turn to your right and walk back to the counter where the microwave is.
Place the potato in the microwave, wait a moment, then remove the potato from the microwave.
Turn towards your left, and walk towards the coffee pot.
Place the potato slice on the counter top, in front of the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato slice on the counter, in front of a coffee pot.

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter, then turn right.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Slice the potato in the right sink basin into many slices.
Look up at the kitchen sink.
Put the knife point down into the left middle side of the rightmost sink basin.
Look down at the kitchen sink.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato out of the sink basin.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the microwave.
Heat up the potato slice in the microwave for a couple seconds, then take the potato slice out of the microwave and close the microwave door.
Turn left and walk up to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Put the heated potato slice on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward and then turn to the counter on the right.
Pick up the big knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink that is on the right.
Use the knife to cut the potato in the right side of the sink into slices.
Raise the knife up in the air some.
Put the knife in the sink on the left side of the sliced potato.
Look down into the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and then head to the left to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, close the microwave, turn it on to cook, then open the microwave and remove the potato.
Turn to the left and go forward toward the coffee pot.
Put the potato on the counter in front of the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter in front of you
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn around and head to the sink
Cut the potato in the sink into slices
Look up at the sink
Put the knife down in the sink
Look down at the sink
Grab one of the potato slices
Turn around and head to the microwave
Heat the potato in the microwave and take it out
Turn left and head straight to the counter
Put the potato on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a sliced potato on the counter
